<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 12:30:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度表示准备在边界争端解决后与中国建立商业关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-signals-readiness-pursue-china-business-ties-after-border-row-resolved-2024-12-03/</link><description>印度外长周二表示，印度和中国已完成从喜马拉雅边境最后两个对峙点撤军，两国将以适当的方式考虑双边关系的“其他方面”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 11:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-signals-readiness-pursue-china-business-ties-after-border-row-resolved-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：巴黎沸腾之际，华尔街创历史新高，人民币触及2024年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 11:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国行业机构表示，购买美国芯片“不再安全”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-should-diversify-chip-sources-internet-society-china-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>中国四个顶级行业协会表示，中国企业应该谨慎购买美国芯片，而应该在本地购买。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 10:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-should-diversify-chip-sources-internet-society-china-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉11月份中国产电动汽车销量下降4.3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-drop-43-yy-nov-2024-12-03/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉11月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比下降4.3%至78,856辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:48:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-drop-43-yy-nov-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>贸易摩擦升级 中国禁止向美国出口关键矿产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-bans-exports-gallium-germanium-antimony-us-2024-12-03/</link><description>这些限制针对的是“军民两用”矿物镓、锗和锑，这些矿物既有军事用途，也有民用用途。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-bans-exports-gallium-germanium-antimony-us-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>Nexperia 将遵守美国对中国母公司闻泰科技的限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nexperia-comply-with-us-restrictions-chinese-parent-wingtech-2024-12-03/</link><description>总部位于荷兰的计算机芯片制造商 Nexperia 发言人周二表示，在其中国母公司闻泰科技被列入美国商务部实体名单后，该公司将遵守美国的限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 07:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nexperia-comply-with-us-restrictions-chinese-parent-wingtech-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国芯片公司表示他们可以承受美国新的出口限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-chip-firms-say-they-can-withstand-new-us-export-curbs-2024-12-03/</link><description>芯片公司誓言要加速供应链本地化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 07:36:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-chip-firms-say-they-can-withstand-new-us-export-curbs-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>解说：中国实施矿产出口禁令后，还能如何应对美国芯片限制？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/how-china-could-retaliate-against-new-us-chip-curbs-2024-12-03/</link><description>在美国一天前对中国芯片行业实施限制后，中国禁止向美国出口某些含有关键矿物的商品，同时收紧其他商品的出口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 07:32:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/how-china-could-retaliate-against-new-us-chip-curbs-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔总理转向印度寻求中国经济支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pivot-india-nepal-pm-visits-china-seek-investment-2024-12-03/</link><description>尼泊尔资深共产主义政治家KP Sharma Oli今年第四次担任该国总理，在远离印度势力范围的情况下，本周寻求与北京启动基础设施项目。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 06:10:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pivot-india-nepal-pm-visits-china-seek-investment-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>核协议失败30年后乌克兰敦促北约邀请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-pushes-nato-invite-30-years-after-failed-nuclear-deal-2024-12-03/</link><description>1994年的布达佩斯备忘录让基辅放弃了世界第三大核武库。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 06:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-pushes-nato-invite-30-years-after-failed-nuclear-deal-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国取消对澳大利亚肉类加工商的最终贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-final-trade-restrictions-australian-meat-processors-2024-12-03/</link><description>澳大利亚政府周二表示，中国取消了对澳大利亚两家肉类加工厂的贸易限制，允许全面恢复向该国出口红肉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 05:56:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-final-trade-restrictions-australian-meat-processors-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>香港特首表示高尔夫球场裁决不会影响公共住房计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-says-golf-course-ruling-will-not-hit-plans-public-housing-2024-12-03/</link><description>香港法院领导人李约翰 (John Lee) 周二表示，香港一家法院呼吁就在著名高尔夫球场部分地区建造 12,000 套公共住宅的计划重新进行公众咨询，这不会对该市的 10 年供应目标产生重大影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 05:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-says-golf-course-ruling-will-not-hit-plans-public-housing-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，台湾可能会在本周末开始军事演习，台湾正在密切关注中国航母的动向</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-watching-chinese-carrier-movements-sources-say-war-games-may-start-this-2024-12-03/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，正在监视中国航母的动向，并评估中国的军事活动，因为安全消息人士称，北京可能最早在本周末发起新的军事演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 04:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-watching-chinese-carrier-movements-sources-say-war-games-may-start-this-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>游说团体称，尽管有刺激措施，英国公司仍对中国业务持悲观态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/british-firms-downbeat-about-china-business-despite-stimulus-lobby-group-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>一项调查发现，在华经营的英国公司认为，由于经济形势低迷，过去一年在世界第二大经济体做生意变得更加困难，他们预计这种情况将持续到2025年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 02:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/british-firms-downbeat-about-china-business-despite-stimulus-lobby-group-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲和欧洲股市在美国的带动下上涨，而美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-03/</link><description>科技公司推动华尔街隔夜创下历史新高后，欧洲和亚洲股市周二上涨，而美元在前一天上涨后企稳。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 02:46:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>